| HistoryText             = The Iron Rangers were a private secturity team employed by Hall Industries and outfitted with [[Iron Ranger Armor|biomechanical body armor]] engineered from the [[Carnage (Symbiote) (Earth-616)|Carnage symbiote]] and based on Tony Stark's [[Iron Man Armor]].

The Iron Rangers interfered with Spider-Man's battle with [[Doppelganger (Spider-Man) (Earth-616)|Doppelganger]], seemingly killing it.{{r|Carnage Vol 1 1}}

When the Carnage symbiote reunited with [[Cletus Kasady (Earth-616)|Cletus Kasady]], he used its newfound ability to spawn and control offshoots of itself to seize control of the Iron Rangers, kill them, and merge with their armor to become "Mass Carnage".{{r|Carnage Vol 1 4}}
